overview.en: NIWO is a de-centralized notarized economic ecosystem, which records and shares the output of the system according to the rights and interests of participants, then practices the concept of notarized economy, and ultimately realizes the wealth appreciation of the community of interests.
overview.zh: NIWO是去中心化通证经济生态系统，根据参与者的权益记录共享系统产出，进而践行通证经济理念，最终实现利益共同体的财富增值。
